channel.title: Need Coder For My 317 with 614 Graphics Webclient, Etc!
channel.description:
I host the server, the webclient, etc. I just need a lot of coding done through teamviewer. I'm on pretty much all day on weekdays, (nothing else to do) not too much on weekends though. I am going to be making a donation system, and I can give 50% of profits to whoever wants to help code. If you want to see what my server looks like before you get on, just use this link.
http://rspscoding.org/play.php?server=ShafirScape
Please add me on skype: Master.Ca
I know 50% of what I'm doing for coding. I can make a command but I hate fixing errors.. because it just chains on to another error, another, etc. My old coder quit out of random. He literaly just logged off my teamviewer, blocks me on skype, blocks on facebook. After only like 3 days =o..
I really want iPanel. I need a few bugs fixed, and some commands to work for people with different player rights. I need to learn some teleport commands.
There's more, but that's the most of what I need.
Remember: I will not be giving the source to you if you choose to code for me. You will code through teamviewer, but I will always be available.
